Mufazzal b. `Aumar said, 'Make use of some of the [commodities of this] world to help you in the next world, for I have heard Abu `Aabdallah (AS) [i.e. Imam al-Sadiq] say, 'Make use of some of this [abode] for that one, but do not be a burden on other people.â€™
[Bihar al-Anwar, v. 78, p. 381, no. 1]